(4603, 10, '_blocks_9_header', 'field_681dee0080c58'),
(4604, 10, 'blocks_9_testimonials_0_text', '\"Working with Diaan on our office renovation was a game-changer. Their glazing and ventilation solutions brought in so much natural light and fresh air that our workspace feels entirely transformed. The team was professional, efficient, and paid great attention to detail. Highly recommend them for any modern building project!\"'),
