(274, 1, '2025-05-12 08:51:08', '2025-05-12 08:51:08', '<h2 data-start=\"111\" data-end=\"163\"><strong data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"163\">Here To Know About This Project</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"165\" data-end=\"536\">This is a thoughtfully designed residential project that brings together elegance, functionality, and lasting quality. Diaan played a key role in this development by delivering top-tier solutions in  <strong data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"408\">Railing</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"414\" data-end=\"425\">Windows</strong>. The project emphasizes seamless indoor-outdoor connectivity, natural lighting, and a clean, modern aesthetic.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"538\" data-end=\"882\">Our glazing and ventilation systems were tailored to maximize light and airflow, creating bright, breathable living spaces. The railings added both safety and style to balconies and stairways, while high-performance windows helped improve insulation and reduce external noise. Every installation was done with precision and attention to detail.</p>', 'Project @ Bhuatn', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'modified-roofing__trashed', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:00:44', '2025-05-20 10:00:44', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?post_type=project&#038;p=274', 8, 'project', '', 0),
