(276, 1, '2025-05-12 08:52:25', '2025-05-12 08:52:25', '<h2 data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"211\"><strong data-start=\"158\" data-end=\"211\">Here To Know About This Project – Chitvan Society</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"213\" data-end=\"578\">Chitvan Society is a well-planned residential community designed to offer a peaceful and functional living experience. Diaan was proud to contribute to this project with our trusted expertise in <strong data-start=\"408\" data-end=\"435\">Glazing and Ventilation</strong>, <strong data-start=\"437\" data-end=\"448\">Railing</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"465\">Windows</strong>. The project focuses on creating bright, well-ventilated spaces that balance comfort, safety, and visual appeal.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"580\" data-end=\"927\">We provided durable, energy-efficient windows that enhanced both aesthetics and performance. Our custom railings added a clean and modern look to balconies and common areas while ensuring safety for residents. The glazing and ventilation solutions were designed to improve natural airflow and light, contributing to a healthier living environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-start=\"934\" data-end=\"961\"><strong data-start=\"941\" data-end=\"961\">Management Style</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1365\">For Chitvan Society, Diaan adopted a collaborative and detail-driven management approach. From initial planning to final handover, our team worked closely with the developers and site engineers to ensure every installation met the project\'s standards and timeline. Our proactive site management and consistent quality checks ensured smooth execution and long-lasting results that residents can rely on.</p>', 'Chitvan Society', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'modified-roofing-2__trashed', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:00:44', '2025-05-20 10:00:44', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?post_type=project&#038;p=276', 7, 'project', '', 0),
