(280, 1, '2025-05-12 08:54:47', '2025-05-12 08:54:47', '<h2 data-start=\"125\" data-end=\"181\"><strong data-start=\"131\" data-end=\"181\">Here To Know About This Project – Akshar ILand</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"183\" data-end=\"555\">Akshar ILand is a landmark development that redefines urban living with a focus on innovation and comfort. Diaan was proud to contribute to this project with our specialized services in <strong data-start=\"369\" data-end=\"396\">Glazing and Ventilation</strong>, <strong data-start=\"398\" data-end=\"409\">Railing</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"415\" data-end=\"426\">Windows</strong>. The design prioritizes spaciousness, energy efficiency, and visual harmony, making it a standout structure in its surroundings.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"557\" data-end=\"875\">Large glass panels bring in ample daylight, while the ventilation systems ensure a fresh and healthy environment throughout the property. Stylish and sturdy railings add a refined touch to balconies and staircases, while the windows were selected not only for performance but also for their modern look and durability.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"909\"><strong data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"909\">Management Style</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"911\" data-end=\"1373\">For the Akshar ILand project, Diaan followed a highly coordinated and proactive management approach. We collaborated closely with architects and engineers to align with the project’s timeline and design vision. Our team paid close attention to detail, ensured quality checks at every stage, and responded swiftly to on-site requirements. This approach helped deliver a smooth execution and a polished final result that met both functional needs and design goals.</p>', 'Akshar ILand', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'akshar-iland__trashed', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:00:41', '2025-05-20 10:00:41', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?post_type=project&#038;p=280', 1, 'project', '', 0),
