(282, 1, '2025-05-12 08:55:22', '2025-05-12 08:55:22', '<h2 data-start=\"91\" data-end=\"150\"><strong data-start=\"97\" data-end=\"150\">Here To Know About This Project – Silver Radience</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"573\">Silver Radience is a stunning example of modern architecture combined with smart functionality. Diaan provided expert services in <strong data-start=\"282\" data-end=\"309\">Glazing and Ventilation</strong>, <strong data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"322\">Railing</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"328\" data-end=\"339\">Windows</strong>, helping to bring the project’s design to life. The building features clean lines, bright interiors, and a strong emphasis on natural light and airflow. Every element was carefully selected to enhance both aesthetics and performance.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"575\" data-end=\"871\">This project was designed to offer comfort, safety, and style. From spacious balconies with sleek railings to large, energy-efficient windows, every detail reflects thoughtful planning and high-quality execution. The end result is a residential space that feels open, inviting, and built to last.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-start=\"878\" data-end=\"905\"><strong data-start=\"885\" data-end=\"905\">Management Style</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"1325\">The Silver Radience project was managed with a hands-on, detail-focused approach. Diaan worked closely with the project team to ensure smooth communication, timely installation, and consistent quality. Our team stayed involved at every stage—planning, execution, and final inspection—to make sure everything met the highest standards. The project reflects our commitment to precision, reliability, and long-term value.</p>', 'Silver Radience', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'silver-radience__trashed', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:00:42', '2025-05-20 10:00:42', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?post_type=project&#038;p=282', 2, 'project', '', 0),
