(284, 1, '2025-05-12 08:55:51', '2025-05-12 08:55:51', '<h2 data-start=\"92\" data-end=\"145\"><strong data-start=\"98\" data-end=\"145\">Here To Know About This Project – HR ELANZA</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"147\" data-end=\"678\">The HR ELANZA project stands as a modern architectural marvel where innovation meets functionality. With Diaan’s expert craftsmanship in <strong data-start=\"284\" data-end=\"311\">Glazing and Ventilation</strong>, <strong data-start=\"313\" data-end=\"324\">Railing</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"330\" data-end=\"341\">Windows</strong>, the project reflects sleek design, structural integrity, and energy-efficient solutions. The property features high-end finishes and thoughtful design.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1003\" data-end=\"1030\"><strong data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1030\">Management Style</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"1032\" data-end=\"1360\">The HR ELANZA project was executed with a collaborative, detail-oriented approach. Diaan coordinated closely with architects, engineers, and on-site teams to ensure timely delivery and premium-quality execution. Every decision was driven by performance, durability, and aesthetic harmony with the building’s contemporary vision.</p>', 'HR ELANZA', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hr-elanza__trashed', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:00:37', '2025-05-20 10:00:37', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?post_type=project&#038;p=284', 0, 'project', '', 0),
