(382, 1, '2025-05-13 11:55:23', '2025-05-13 11:55:23', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">In the world of modern architecture, less is more. Fix windows from Diaan embrace this philosophy by offering clear, uninterrupted views with zero moving parts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Benefits of Fix Windows:</h3>\r\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Unmatched Clarity</strong>: Since they don’t open, there are no visible hardware or seals obstructing the view.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficient</strong>: They are sealed shut, offering excellent insulation against heat, cold, and noise.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low Maintenance</strong>: With no hinges or sliders to worry about, maintenance is a breeze.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFix windows are ideal for high-rise buildings, commercial facades, and minimalist home interiors. With Diaan, you can customize size, frame material, and glass type to match your project perfectly.', 'Fix Windows: A Minimalist’s Dream for Clean Views and Energy Efficiency', 'With Diaan, you can customize size, frame material, and glass type to match your project perfectly.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'correct-execution-ensures-victory-5', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:33:17', '2025-05-20 10:33:17', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?p=382', 0, 'post', '', 0),
