(425, 1, '2025-05-15 13:41:16', '2025-05-15 13:41:16', '<h2 data-start=\"111\" data-end=\"163\"><strong data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"163\">Here To Know About This Project</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"165\" data-end=\"536\">This is a thoughtfully designed residential project that brings together elegance, functionality, and lasting quality. Diaan played a key role in this development by delivering top-tier solutions in <strong data-start=\"368\" data-end=\"395\">Glazing and Ventilation</strong>, <strong data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"408\">Railing</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"414\" data-end=\"425\">Windows</strong>. The project emphasizes seamless indoor-outdoor connectivity, natural lighting, and a clean, modern aesthetic.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"538\" data-end=\"882\">Our glazing and ventilation systems were tailored to maximize light and airflow, creating bright, breathable living spaces. The railings added both safety and style to balconies and stairways, while high-performance windows helped improve insulation and reduce external noise. Every installation was done with precision and attention to detail.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"887\" />\r\n\r\n<h2 data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"916\"><strong data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"916\">Management Style</strong></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"918\" data-end=\"1344\">This project was managed with a strong focus on quality, coordination, and timely delivery. Diaan maintained constant communication with the construction team to align with the project goals and timelines. Our on-site team ensured smooth installation, minimal disruption, and full compliance with safety standards. The result is a refined, reliable finish that reflects Diaan’s commitment to excellence at every stage.</p>', 'Project @ Baroda', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'project-baroda__trashed', '', '', '2025-05-20 10:00:42', '2025-05-20 10:00:42', '', 0, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?post_type=project&#038;p=425', 4, 'proj