(446, 1, '2025-05-15 14:18:19', '2025-05-15 14:18:19', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Sliding windows are all about ease and practicality. They’re a favorite in modern construction due to their sleek design and space-saving functionality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why Choose Sliding Windows:</h3>\r\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Space-Saving</strong>: No need for extra clearance to open or close.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Easy to Operate</strong>: Glides effortlessly on tracks, ideal for daily use.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ideal for Compact Spaces</strong>: Perfect for apartments, kitchens, and bathrooms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDiaan’s sliding windows are engineered with premium rollers and secure locking systems to ensure both functionality and safety. Choose from a range of frames and glass options to suit any architectural style.', 'Sliding Windows by Diaan: Smooth Functionality Meets Elegant Design', 'Proin efficitur, mauris vel condimentum pulvinar, velit orci consectetur ligula.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '379-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-15 14:18:19', '2025-05-15 14:18:19', '', 379, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?p=446', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(447, 1, '2025-05-15 14:21:28', '2025-05-15 14:21:28', 'When it comes to designing modern buildings, whether residential or commercial, the importance of <strong data-start=\"258\" data-end=\"285\">glazing and ventilation</strong> cannot be overstated. At <strong data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"320\">Diaan</strong>, we specialize in delivering high-performance glazing and ventilation solutions that not only enhance the visual appeal of your property but also significantly improve comfort, efficiency, and air quality.\n<h2 data-start=\"533\" data-end=\"563\"><strong data-start=\"540\" data-end=\"563\">Why Glazing Matters</strong></h2>\n<p data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"710\">Glazing is far more than just glass. It’s a smart design feature that affects how your building performs in terms of heat, light, and insulation.</p>\n\n<h3 data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"740\">Key Benefits of Glazing:</h3>\n<ul data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"1219\">\n 	<li data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"886\">\n<p data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"886\"><strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"764\">Energy Efficiency</strong>: Proper glazing reduces heat transfer, keeping interiors cooler in summer and warmer in winter—cutting down energy bills.</p>\n</li>\n 	<li data-start=\"887\" data-end=\"1028\">\n<p data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"1028\"><strong data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"906\">Natural Light</strong>: Well-placed glazing can flood a space with natural light, improving mood and reducing dependence on artificial lighting.</p>\n</li>\n 	<li data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1143\">\n<p data-start=\"1031\" data-end=\"1143\"><strong data-start=\"1031\" data-end=\"1050\">Noise Reduction</strong>: High-quality glass helps reduce outside noise, creating a more peaceful indoor environment.</p>\n</li>\n 	<li data-start=\"1144\" data-end=\"1219\">\n<p data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1219\"><strong data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1160\">Aesthetics</strong>: Glazing adds a sleek, modern look to any building facade.</p>\