(453, 1, '2025-05-15 14:29:00', '2025-05-15 14:29:00', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">When designing or renovating a space, windows are often the unsung heroes. They provide light, air, views, and can completely transform the mood of a room. At Diaan, we offer a wide range of high-quality window types, including Fix Windows, Sliding Windows, Casement Windows, and Slide &amp; Fold systems. But which one is right for your space?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Fix Windows: For Clear Views and Zero Maintenance</h3>\r\nFix windows are stationary and do not open. They are ideal for areas where ventilation isn\'t necessary but where you want to frame a view or let in natural light. Perfect for living rooms, stairwells, or commercial spaces.\r\n<h3>Sliding Windows: Smooth Operation in Tight Spaces</h3>\r\nSliding windows open horizontally and are great for spaces where swinging sashes are impractical. They are low-maintenance, easy to operate, and suitable for kitchens, bathrooms, and urban apartments.\r\n<h3>Casement Windows: Ventilation with a View</h3>\r\nCasement windows open outwards like a door, offering maximum airflow. They’re perfect for areas that require regular ventilation and unobstructed outside views.\r\n<h3>Slide &amp; Fold: Indoor-Outdoor Integration</h3>\r\nThese are large openings that fold away completely, ideal for connecting interiors with outdoor spaces. Commonly used in patios, balconies, and even conference rooms.\r\n\r\nChoosing the right window depends on your needs—whether it’s light, air, aesthetics, or access. At Diaan, we help you make the right choice based on function, design, and durability.', 'Choosing the Right Window Style for Your Space: A Complete Guide by Diaan', 'At Diaan, we offer a wide range of high-quality window types, including Fix Windows, Sliding Windows, Casement Windows, and Slide & Fold systems.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '385-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-15 14:29:00', '2025-05-15 14:29:00', '', 385, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?p=453', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(454, 1, '2025-05-15 14:29:22', '2025-05-15 14:29:22', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">In the world of modern architecture, less is more. Fix windows from Diaan embrace this philosophy by offering clear, uninterrupted views with zero moving parts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Benefits of Fix Windows:</h3>\r\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Unmatched Clarity</strong>: Since they don’t open, there are no visible hardware or seals obstructing the view.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficient</strong>: They are sealed shut, offering excellent insulation against heat, cold, and noise.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low Maintenance</strong>: With no hinges or sliders to worry about, maintenance is a breeze.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFix windows are ideal for high-rise buildings, commercial facades, and minimalist home interiors. With Diaan, you can customize size, frame material, and glass type to match your project perfectly.', 'Fix Windows: A Minimalist’s Dream for Clean Views and Energy Efficiency', 'With Diaan, you can customize size, frame material, and glass type to match your project perfectly.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '382-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-15 14:29:22', '2025-05-15 14:29:22', '', 382, 'https://www.inboundweb.in/diaan/?p=454', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
